qMsg.qv: ='Please make a selection to filter your results.'

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=num(
COUNT({<%DateKey=, CareType={'AL','LG'},LastStepDate={"<$(=Date(today()-7))"},Status={'Hot', 'Closing','Reserved'}, FactType={'1'}> 
+
<%DateKey=, CareType={'IL'}, LastStepDate={"<$(=Date(today()-14))"},Status={'Hot', 'Closing','Reserved'},  FactType={'1'}>
+
<%DateKey=, CareType={'AL','LG'},LastStepDate={"<$(=Date(today()-21))"},Status={'Reserved'},  FactType={'1'}>
+
<%DateKey=, CareType={'AL','LG'},LastStepDate={"<$(=Date(today()-7))"},Status={'Hot', 'Closing'}, FactType={'1'}>
+
<%DateKey=, CareType={'IL'}, LastStepDate={"<$(=Date(today()-14))"},Status={'Hot', 'Closing'},  FactType={'1'}>
+
<%DateKey=, DateOfInquiry={"<$(=Date(today()-14))"},Status={'New Lead'}, FactType={'1'}>}DISTINCT(%InquiryID)),'#,##0.;(#,##0.)')

&
' At Risk Inquiries (Hot, Closing, Reserved)'
'"At Risk" Hot, Closing, and Reserved inquiries haven???t been contacted in 7 days (AL/MC) or in 14 days (IL) or in 21 days (Reserved at Unoccupied New Devs). New Leads older than 14 days.'

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Inquiries that are marked "active" in CRM but have a last update date prior to today'

qMsg.qv: ='Please make a selection to filter your results.'

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=num(Count({<ActiveCRMStatus={'Active'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'1'}, %DateKey-={">=$(=Date(Today()-1))"}>
+<ActiveCRMStatus={'Active'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'1'}, %DateKey-={">=$(=Date(today()))<$(=Date(Today()-1))"}>}Distinct %InquiryID)
-
Count({<ActiveCRMStatus={'Active'},NextStep={'*'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'1'}, %DateKey-={">=$(=Date(Today()-1))"}>
+<ActiveCRMStatus={'Active'},NextStep={'*'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'1'}, %DateKey-={">=$(=Date(today()))<$(=Date(Today()-1))"}>
+<ActiveCRMStatus={'Active'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'1'}, %DateKey-={">=$(=Date(today()))<$(=Date(Today()-1))"}, LateNightLeadFlg={'1'} >}Distinct %InquiryID),'##,##0')&

' Active Inquiries without Next Step'
'Inquiries that are marked "active" in CRM but do not have a next step indicated'

qMsg.qv: ='Please make a selection to filter your results.'

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=num(
	Count({<Status-={'Lost','Not Qualified','Moved In','Moved Out','Moved Back', 'Deceased','Deceased - Inquiry', 'Unable To Qualify'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'13'}, MessageState-={'Complete','Incomplete','Late','Left Message','Not Applicable'}>
		+<Status-={'Lost','Not Qualified','Moved In','Moved Out','Moved Back', 'Deceased','Deceased - Inquiry', 'Unable To Qualify'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'13'}, MessageState-={'Complete','Late','Left Message','Missed','Not Applicable'}, 
        	FollowUpEffectiveDT={"<=$(=Date(Today()-1))"}>} %InquiryID)
 	-
	Count({<Status-={'Lost','Not Qualified','Moved In','Moved Out','Moved Back', 'Deceased','Deceased - Inquiry', 'Unable To Qualify'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'13'}, 
		MessageState-={'Complete','Incomplete','Late','Left Message','Not Applicable'}, NextClosingStep={'*'}>
		+<Status-={'Lost','Not Qualified','Moved In','Moved Out','Moved Back', 'Deceased','Deceased - Inquiry', 'Unable To Qualify'},CareType=,RoomTypeStyleCode=, FactType={'13'}, 
        MessageState-={'Complete','Late','Left Message','Missed','Not Applicable'}, FollowUpEffectiveDT={"<=$(=Date(Today()-1))"}, NextClosingStep={'*'}>} %InquiryID),'#,##0.;(#,##0.)')

&
 ' 24h Tour Confirmation Missed'
'Active Inquiry Scheduled Tours ' & Date(Today()-3) & ' - ' & Date(Today()+7) & ' | Yellow indicates a future tour without a scheduled confirmation.'
